version: 1.0.0
date-released: "2026-03-14"
doi: 10.5281/zenodo.19041570
abstract: >-
  OASIS is a self-hosted, open-source platform for conducting AI-powered
  conversational interviews. It supports voice and text modalities,
  semi-structured interview guides, multi-provider LLM pipelines, and
  real-time transcript diarisation. Built for survey researchers and
  qualitative methodologists who need full control over their data and
  infrastructure.
keywords:
  - conversational AI
